    General Stores in Bhuleshwar, Mumbai

    (322 Ratings & Reviews) 4.2 Average Ratings

    General Stores in Bhuleshwar, Mumbai

    Commonly known as 'kiranas' in the local parlance, mom-n-pop shops are nothing but general stores. There's bound to be a general shop located at every other corner of any neighbourhood. In certain metros and cities, a general store can also be a part of a pharmacy or medicine shop. Any of these stores house a vast variety of products ranging from loose grains and pulses to cosmetics. A modern general store may have air-conditioning, a wider range of products and services that local shops may not offer. Following the traditional system, most serve customers through a counter system, certain stores encourage self-service for their customers, by following a more modern system. These store owners work in conjunction with wholesalers, distributors, and retailers forming a wide network in the city or town. Please scroll up to find a list of General Stores in Bhuleshwar, Mumbai.
